            "value": "**Pi 0.73.1 вАФ 3 highlights**\n\n- `pi update --self` now handles the package rename from `@mariozechner/pi-coding-agent` to `@earendil-works/pi-coding-agent`, so existing global installs migrate via the normal self-update flow.\n- OAuth providers can present multiple login choices through `/login` for provider-specific interactive sign-in.\n- `models.json` now accepts comments and trailing commas (JSONC), making custom provider/model configuration easier to maintain."
